		{"id":"deriver-tools","type":"text","text":"# Layer 3 dumb tools: 11 built capabilities\n\nIndex: build_vault_index.py\nIntegrity: link_reference_checker.py, capture_integrity_checker.py\nOrientation: build_orientation_digest.py\nFreshness: derived_staleness_signal.py\nSearch: build_term_cooccurrence.py, missed_retrieval_detector.py, vault_search.py, two_lane_search.py\nGovernance: source_census.py, trigger_watcher.py, session_link_index.py\n\nDumb rule: compute and flag; never fix.","x":560,"y":20,"width":500,"height":330},
